<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Automation</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Automations built for real service operations
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
        Create powerful workflows that run automatically across your Clinic or Commercial Platform — from submissions and bookings to staff notifications, reporting, and internal operations. No code required.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white pb-24 sm:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-base/7 text-gray-600">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Automate the repetitive</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Free your team from manual tasks and let your operations run on autopilot. Our automation engine connects your data, triggers actions, and keeps your workflows moving without delays.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          From intake submissions to booking confirmations, every workflow can be automated with precision — helping clinics and commercial teams save time and reduce errors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Designed for flexibility</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Build simple or multi-step workflows using intuitive rules and triggers. Automations adapt to your business logic, staff structure, and bilingual workflows (EN/ES).
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Whether you're a single-location business or a growing multi-location operation, our automation tools scale with you.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Capabilities</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Powerful automation tools
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Trigger-Based Workflows</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Start automations when submissions arrive, bookings are created, staff actions occur, or system events trigger.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Email & SMS Notifications</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Automatically notify customers or staff in English or Spanish when key actions happen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Routing</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Send submissions, bookings, or tasks to the right staff, department, or location instantly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Conditional Logic</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Build smart workflows that adapt based on service type, form data, staff availability, or customer behavior.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Multi-Step Sequences</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Chain actions together to create powerful, multi-stage workflows for onboarding, follow-ups, and internal processes.
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Integrations</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Connect with external tools, APIs, and internal modules to extend your automation capabilities.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
