        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Automatically route new leads or submissions into your CRM and notify the right staff instantly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
