        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Trigger welcome messages, assign staff tasks, and prepare accounts automatically after a submission or booking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Internal Notifications</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
