        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Automated Reporting</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Generate daily, weekly, or monthly reports and deliver them automatically to your team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Form Routing</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Route submissions to the correct department, staff member, or location based on form data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Customer Follow-Ups</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Trigger follow-up messages, reminders, or tasks based on customer actions or inactivity.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-sky-500 py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:col-span-7">
